hactool
------------------------------------------
hactool is a tool to view information about, decrypt, and extract common file
formats for the Nintendo Switch, especially Nintendo Content Archives.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.2-1
  libcjson1-1.7.12-1bl1
  libgcc1-7.4.0-1
  liblz4_1-1.7.5-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.14.5-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-7.4.0-1
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/SciresM/hactool

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/SciresM/hactool/archive/1.3.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack hactool-1.3.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./hactool-1.3.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/hactool-1.3.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/hactool-1.3.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(hactool)
  /usr/bin/hactool.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/hactool.README
  /usr/share/doc/hactool/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/hactool/README.md

------------------

